briefdescription.para: Identifier of the owner merchant.
Identifier of the product type. Current defined types: 1 = booking product 2 = real estate product 3 = grouping product of the types specified above
Identifier of the subscription.
Reference of the item useful for external service.
Name of the product from the default language of subscription.
Description of the product from the default language of subscription.
If this property is set to true, the product is viewable in the public area.
Priority of the item.
Name of the main image that is hosted from the CDN.
Geographic address.
Unique code of a state taken from GeoNames.
Name of the state/country taken from GeoNames, if StateId is defined.
Unique code of a region/districy/federal state taken from GeoNames.
Name of the region/districy/federal state taken from GeoNames, if RegionId is defined.
Identifier of a subscription geographic zone.
Name of the subscription geographic zone (like city district or macro-region), if ZoneId is defined.
Unique code of a city taken from GeoNames.
Name of the city taken from GeoNames, if CityId is defined.
Zip code or postal code.
Latitude.
Logitude.
Internal rating of the product.
Identifier of the product category with the highest priority and the greates level, if it has at least one.
Array of identifiers of descriptive services joined by a comma.
If the property is defined, identifies the expiration date of validation for the product.
Identifier of the group.
Cancellation policy used by the product.
A generic sellable product or item that groups some others, it depends on the type.
